Package: cart
Type: Package
Title: Diffusion-based cartograms
Version: 0.3.1
Date: 2013-04-22
Author: Thomas Zumbrunn <thomas@zumbrunn.name>
Maintainer: Thomas Zumbrunn <thomas@zumbrunn.name>
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas", "Zumbrunn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "thomas@zumbrunn.name"), person("David H.", "Brown", role = c("ctb")))
Description: Produce density-equalising maps or "cartograms" based on the
    diffusion-based method by Michael T. Gastner and Mark E. J. Newman and an
    implementation by Mark E. J. Newman
    (http://people.cas.sc.edu/hardistf/cartograms/).
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15.0)
Imports:
    maps (>= 2.2-5),
    maptools (>= 0.8-14),
    rdyncall (>= 0.7.5),
    sp (>= 1.0-5)
Suggests:
    mapdata,
    methods,
    graphics
SystemRequirements: fftw3 (http://www.fftw.org)
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/thomaszumbrunn/cart/
BugReports: https://github.com/thomaszumbrunn/cart/issues
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Encoding: UTF-8
Collate:
    'cart.R'
